{"tid":621453,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"新牌仔想買車 有咩要注意","createTime":"2018-04-08T10:26:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T05:27:59.000Z","uid":93905,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"53f5fe60b2ea5548723cbb9ec65736792a740267","tid":621453,"uid":93905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:26:16.000Z","msg":"想買左架2手車<br />\n約左賣家之後係咪通常會渣佢架車兜個圈<br />\n定係叫佢拎去車房度驗左先<br />\n<br />\n同埋有咩手續要搞<br />\n例如上律師師或者運輸署改返個名 同買保險續牌費個d?"},{"pid":"7678dac903a1d372c73e71bdb807b7267d2c92d4","tid":621453,"uid":93905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:26:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想買架2手車<br />\n約左賣家之後係咪通常會渣佢架車兜個圈<br />\n定係叫佢拎去車房度驗左先<br />\n<br />\n同埋有咩手續要搞<br />\n例如上律師師或者運輸署改返個名 同買保險續牌費個d?</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a73e19f7bb50995f2f0e9521b2723518528d0f39","tid":621453,"uid":3912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:55:26.000Z","msg":"揾個識車同你一齊去試，新仔二手車操車唔使太大要求 基本嘢踩快少少然後試剎車有冇問題，再睇下有冇走呔<br />\n冇乜問題就去上架睇下，上架費你出，掂就運吉處過户，過户費都係你出，跟手找埋尾數攞車正式做車主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb95feb2e654ccb750edeaa37211408ee9f67b7","tid":621453,"uid":10133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:15:23.000Z","msg":"試車試清楚，大油大brake"},{"pid":"8c1dabad5b5fdcbde35f37ca6a6f020aaf0e22c6","tid":621453,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T23:42:40.000Z","msg":"行highway睇有無震"},{"pid":"b03f95bcbae51da3cfb8e6a17e447928bb49282d","tid":621453,"uid":51105,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:03:34.000Z","msg":"買二手車好似正常唔會俾買家揸<br />\n係賣家試俾你睇多（好似係）<br />\n車行佬就另計"},{"pid":"6b44c72f3a1f03ec94acbea213c2c73f3ad055e0","tid":621453,"uid":54081,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b03f95bcbae51da3cfb8e6a17e447928bb49282d","tid":621453,"uid":51105,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:03:34.000Z","msg":"買二手車好似正常唔會俾買家揸<br />\n係賣家試俾你睇多（好似係）<br />\n車行佬就另計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:14:59.000Z","msg":"正常係嘅，保險問題"},{"pid":"4a515e0618ac27bc27977c85d79b997817fc94fd","tid":621453,"uid":35864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:59:09.000Z","msg":"試下地板油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3edf2732be860bb56b2bb9890bd7c5c783599e70","tid":621453,"uid":108244,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:32:17.000Z","msg":"05年車7字買唔買得過？如果買我就係第8字<br />\n因為睇完車覺得ok，想上架睇埋就扑鎚"},{"pid":"67e84e1e3b0548778810c905168488e74e00e89c","tid":621453,"uid":30895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3edf2732be860bb56b2bb9890bd7c5c783599e70","tid":621453,"uid":108244,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:32:17.000Z","msg":"05年車7字買唔買得過？如果買我就係第8字<br />\n因為睇完車覺得ok，想上架睇埋就扑鎚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:34:09.000Z","msg":"7字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔驗都擺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩車嚟架，買左保險未"},{"pid":"faa229e5fcfddff73ef780b07f2a9cabf79e503a","tid":621453,"uid":19932,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:40:37.000Z","msg":"唔洗下下負評嘅 各位車手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我答你<br />\n一開始咪埋位睇下車身呀 軚呀 車內點先 有無咩壞 試下郁下座位 <br />\n無問題就 就上車試 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好一上車就開冷氣</span>我試就一定係刹車先 刹車無問題先揸得開心。比下油 收下油 唔洗同佢慳 睇下去得順唔順 收放正唔正常先<br />\n再掂就開冷氣 行埋斜路。<br />\n無問題就都可以揾車佬上架驗。"},{"pid":"177e26b114905f39b3441f5fb1e1a4e958a016f1","tid":621453,"uid":19932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:42:11.000Z","msg":"至於你話保險出車個part我就唔多熟啦 交比其他巴打答。"},{"pid":"a689ae9c6d2fb1007df62f84b97ac2ff1131696a","tid":621453,"uid":108244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"